claim.claim-text:
A marine seismic streamer configuration, comprising:
a streamer (218);
one or more pressure signal gradient measuring devices (334) disposed on the streamer, wherein each pressure signal gradient measuring device comprises a first receiver, a second receiver and a third receiver disposed in a triangular configuration;
a processor (530); and
a memory (533) comprising program instructions executable by the processor (530) to compute pressure signal gradients between the pressure signals recorded at the first receiver, at the second receiver and at the third receiver.
